{"tid":1534632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"830麻包袋單嘢係邊個做，堅定流都唔重要","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:45:12.000Z","uid":6033,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"77197df120fbb294e95cc085f425334a96267ad4","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"當大家都咁仇恨黑警，咁想打柒佢哋，但係真係有麻包袋事件出現嘅時候（唔理真定假）就個個出晒嚟質疑係咪班狗自編自導自演，唔係話大家保持思考理性唔好，但係我想問下各位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解見到有狗比人麻包袋第一時間唔係開心，而係想推個波比人？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係咪唔想整污糟自己隻手？係咪覺得所有「過激」嘅嘢都係班狗搵臥底做嚟暗算自己？係咪驚咁樣做會令失去民意？<br />\n<br />\n潔癖少陣啦，係你哋自己未接受到咋，所以你哋先會係咁搵藉口唔肯接受有手足麻包袋黑警呢個可能性<br />\n<br />\n政府係唔會自己退讓，只有行動不斷升級先可以比到更多壓力政府，抗爭越來越激烈只係時間嘅問題，而因為現時我哋冇對等嘅武力正面對抗黑警，抗爭日後亦會開始使用一啲比較卑鄙嘅手法，包括精神攻擊（禍必及家人）同埋麻包袋<br />\n如果你哋重係比自己嘅道德枷鎖拘束住，抗爭就難以繼續升級，班狗就真係唔撚會驚我哋，最後只會一敗塗地<br />\n<br />\n記住抗爭一開始嘅口號<br />\n不篤灰不割席不指責 兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n<br />\n你此時此刻接受唔到冇問題，但係唔好污名化任何抗爭嘅行動，唔好將所有自己唔想接受嘅嘢推比黑警，抗爭係唔需要底線，請大家銘記於心<br />\n<br />\n呢個post雖然好撚長，但係希望大家可以睇晒佢，自己再作思考<br />\n［超長文］前線革命宣言：830隻狗係我地斬嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533987</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8bd55b12480de4b2924e24ace0875e7801c068d","tid":1534632,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a96ff960a5b73851231cb78eba760ae1354a464d","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"63f387dc6c8894884b6525a5c84324932e76e159","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"順便幫手推下9月7 機埸見"},{"pid":"0516c35714e055434702549c80312e8b0f03f82b","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"07176dd724ba173f77e35ce6b0fee93199231261","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"1f74de4a7b3b7f3bb2f2d9652518a17644154b3e","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"318b275b4de47f08cb0affebe2543a4858d8174d","tid":1534632,"uid":254703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0037ce4c59e7168d46cd54802e2701cb0e996077","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"fd8b0dfd8c8d164a39aeec0c5ce423278dabea25","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"f6b673927b33c28075719f6a1da14c29b5ca21cf","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"318b275b4de47f08cb0affebe2543a4858d8174d","tid":1534632,"uid":254703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"終於有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fb230843be65005a8d40bd4e83f8ad85c08b9d","tid":1534632,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"收到風何君堯做"},{"pid":"bdaf72048b62a72c0bfc8146786bf327aa2b9fff","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45fb230843be65005a8d40bd4e83f8ad85c08b9d","tid":1534632,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"收到風何君堯做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"收陣皮啦你，一日到黑都剩係識散播謠言<br />\n永遠有行動升級就一定有啲人衝出嚟推個波比對家<br />\n最後啲傻鳩藍絲就一樣會當係我地手足做，自己友就信撚到十足然後日撚日喺度散播係有鬼做，磨滅行動升級嘅契機"},{"pid":"932ee27e9394afcad53bc94a30002137a927defb","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"97f106377f1070b70063681efc6d0685c2ca83a2","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"07ac09e0bd7afb9e9d4d1d89e74e63e6a05a5b3b","tid":1534632,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"俾狗封鎖消息<br />\n肯定斬到好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家仲未有人落網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89785cce2153266b9613cff135a9b2994b63575","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"抗爭無底線"},{"pid":"c9333a5d8001556769142df187012d720617a410","tid":1534632,"uid":187950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"咁係好可疑"},{"pid":"e7ce1158bef546ab614769c62faef245d43a94a4","tid":1534632,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"唔係 而係單野一開始就太多疑點<br />\n<br />\n理性上好難當係示威者做（雖然係都唔出奇）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起7月有單灣仔有條友比人𠝹頸死左<br />\n個個都話係老豆搵仔"},{"pid":"501ba2220416c31443be784a081f7b92be9659d5","tid":1534632,"uid":77010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:18:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有好多人覺得有退路</span></span>"},{"pid":"78a788cfc05427ce9f51440e8a89eb98d4f4996e","tid":1534632,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ce1158bef546ab614769c62faef245d43a94a4","tid":1534632,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"唔係 而係單野一開始就太多疑點<br />\n<br />\n理性上好難當係示威者做（雖然係都唔出奇）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起7月有單灣仔有條友比人𠝹頸死左<br />\n個個都話係老豆搵仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"其實我講嗰啲嘢唔單止係講緊830，重有之前有出現過擺明屈鳩對家嗰啲post，一開始出petrol bomb都有班友乜都唔理就話係一定係鬼做之類嘅嘢<br />\n我覺得此風不可長"},{"pid":"78dca3a40e2aa8eef926063d2c58b91fae457098","tid":1534632,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢邊個做，最緊要係隻狗見紅"},{"pid":"70008dd54e8cf403f0324b19b8fc40e0174dc3ec","tid":1534632,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0c57c422891f8e34ede0b6e0da2bd04f29b345","tid":1534632,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e438bf642d729b17adb8da8ef07be70bc358d2ce","tid":1534632,"uid":147620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"重點係 麻包袋仲未比人拉 即係安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}